  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Wild Planet, an immersive open-world survival experience that invites you to embark on a journey of exploration and discovery like no other. Cast away on a mysterious planet alone or with your crew, you must harness your ingenuity and teamwork to thrive amidst its untamed wilderness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e40fb4d7077689f69a23e044a1f8ca0a.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e40fb4d7077689f69a23e044a1f8ca0a.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e40fb4d7077689f69a23e044a1f8ca0a.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable in single-player and online co-op. Wild Planet is a stylish low poly open world survival game set in a vast alien planet full of diverse biomes. In the game you’ll explore, hunt the indigenous giant alien bugs, build outposts and craft weapons and equipment as you attempt to survive and build a life for yourself. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/ffb25ac5efd4b9d854bdc45a04cb9568.webp?t=1760010665\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/72e97aff75e0fe660174e302bf11aa61.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/72e97aff75e0fe660174e302bf11aa61.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/72e97aff75e0fe660174e302bf11aa61.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse diverse biomes teeming with life and secrets waiting to be uncovered. From lush forests to desolate wastelands, each corner of the planet offers new wonders to behold and mysteries to unravel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/558e416b0c16221cdf447a80048c38a3.webp?t=1760010665\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/5e8d5eb3d3db40ff653e3808d5ec929e.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/5e8d5eb3d3db40ff653e3808d5ec929e.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/5e8d5eb3d3db40ff653e3808d5ec929e.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct your own sanctuary amidst the sprawling landscapes of the alien world. From humble beginnings to grand fortresses, unleash your creativity as you design and expand your camp to withstand the challenges that lie ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/494097d4ef0e63648e704d379f815a10.webp?t=1760010665\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/ce165c5cc7d4be2b716bebeb799caa09.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/ce165c5cc7d4be2b716bebeb799caa09.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/ce165c5cc7d4be2b716bebeb799caa09.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/d576aaf8a380092824fe16ee2b1a0696.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/d576aaf8a380092824fe16ee2b1a0696.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/d576aaf8a380092824fe16ee2b1a0696.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources from the environment and utilize them to craft essential tools, weapons, and equipment. Whether you're fashioning a sturdy shelter or forging powerful gear to aid you in your adventures, the possibilities are limited only by your imagination. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/84f67d751d0136133902c107b8a5180d.webp?t=1760010665\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e4cc39a10991c375eb96fa432b823f7d.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e4cc39a10991c375eb96fa432b823f7d.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e4cc39a10991c375eb96fa432b823f7d.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into the depths of ancient dungeons, where untold riches and perilous challenges await. Test your mettle against fearsome foes and unravel the mysteries hidden within, but beware – the dangers within are matched only by the rewards they offer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/9f01b747c54b379c107b914a1a424afc.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/9f01b747c54b379c107b914a1a424afc.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/9f01b747c54b379c107b914a1a424afc.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/2513a33a207f8dff9fe72de0e332932f.webp?t=1760010665\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/43d405e7d65442f22a21eaae1a88a3d5.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/43d405e7d65442f22a21eaae1a88a3d5.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/43d405e7d65442f22a21eaae1a88a3d5.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the tranquil ambiance the game, where the beauty of the natural world unfolds before you. With its serene atmosphere and captivating visuals, every moment spent in the game is an opportunity to unwind and escape into a world of adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/d9eecfe76cd566447d6727dc7fe6a8ff.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/d9eecfe76cd566447d6727dc7fe6a8ff.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/d9eecfe76cd566447d6727dc7fe6a8ff.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >we have a unique non-linear storyline driven by dynamic events which will shape your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The players will be confronted by unpredictable hand crafted events driven which will uncover the different paths for the story and lead them through in-game narratives using the strengths of the medium without reliance on cut-scenes.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Wild Planet, an immersive open-world survival experience that invites you to embark on a journey of exploration and discovery like no other. Cast away on a mysterious planet alone or with your crew, you must harness your ingenuity and teamwork to thrive amidst its untamed wilderness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e40fb4d7077689f69a23e044a1f8ca0a.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e40fb4d7077689f69a23e044a1f8ca0a.webm?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/e40fb4d7077689f69a23e044a1f8ca0a.mp4?t=1760010665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable in single-player and online co-op. Wild Planet is a stylish low poly open world survival game set in a vast alien planet full of diverse biomes. In the game you’ll explore, hunt the indigenous giant alien bugs, build outposts and craft weapons and equipment as you attempt to survive and build a life for yourself. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/ffb25ac5efd4b9d854bdc45a04cb9568.webp?t=1760010665\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323060/extras/72e97aff75e0fe660174e302bf11aa61.poster.avif?t=1760010665\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com